description: TEHRAN – Unofficial reports show that pro-reform candidate Masoud Pezeshkian has won 17 million of the votes and his conservative opponent Saeed Jalili has garned about 14 millions of the votes.

description: Some pundits say that Israel (and Hamas) has committed war crimes and crimes against humanity. Others say that Israel is committing genocide before our very eyes. description:
